    <h3>Current undergraduate, graduate, or continuing education student at Umass Amherst</h3>
    <h3>MA EMT certification (EMT-Basic minimum)</h3>
        <!--<p>Want to get EMT-Basic certified? Check out our <%= link_to "class", "/class_info"%></p>-->
