<div>

<h2>How to Become a Full Member</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Make sure you satisfy the membership requirements.</li>
        <li>Make sure you are comfortable with the list of expectations.</li>
        <li>Fill out our <%= link_to "application form", '/join_info/apply' %>.</li>
        <li>Wait for UmassEMS to contact you with the date of the next orientation. These are typically held in early fall or spring.</li>
        <li>Demonstrate sufficient skills during the orientation.</li>
        <li>Start as a probationary member. This means you can now work with a non-probationary member.</li>
        <li>Fulfill the shift, patient contact, and training requirements necessary to become a full member.</li>
        <li>Complete a full member interview before our board of directors.</li>
    </ol>
